<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Scotbank - Your Financial Partner</title>

    {{> Style.hbs}}
</head>

<body>
<!-- Include Sidebar and Header components -->
{{> Sidebar.hbs }}
{{> Header.hbs}}

<!-- Overlay effect when opening sidebar on small screens -->
<div class="w3-overlay w3-hide-large" onclick="w3_close()" style="cursor:pointer" title="close side menu"
     id="myOverlay"></div>


<!-- Main Content -->
<div class="w3-main" style="margin-left:340px;margin-right:40px;margin-bottom: 40px; margin-top: 0;">
    <h1 class="w3-xxxlarge w3-text-red"><b>   </b></h1>
    <h1 class="w3-jumbo"><b>What We Offer</b></h1>
    <hr style="width:50px;border:5px solid red" class="w3-round">
    <p class="w3-large">Welcome to Scotbank, your trusted financial partner in Scotland's central belt since the 1970s. We blend tradition with innovation, now offering digital banking services to better serve you, our valued customers. At our bank, we provide a wide range of financial services to meet your needs. From basic checking and savings accounts to specialized lending options like mortgages and personal loans, we offer convenient digital banking solutions and personalized support from our experienced team. Whether you're saving for the future, managing your day-to-day finances, or pursuing your business goals, we're here to help you every step of the way.</p>


    <div>
        <h1 class="w3-xxxlarge w3-text-red"><b>   </b></h1>
        <h1 class="w3-jumbo"><b>Our Services</b></h1>
        <hr style="width:50px;border:5px solid red" class="w3-round">
        <ul class="w3-ul">
            <li>Everyday Accounts</li>
            <li>Savings Account</li>
            <li>Instant Withdrawals</li>
            <li>Instant Deposit</li>
            <li>Money Transfer</li>
        </ul>
    </div>


    <div class="w3-margin-top">
        <h1 class="w3-xxxlarge w3-text-red"><b>   </b></h1>
        <h1 class="w3-jumbo"><b>Client Testimonials</b></h1>
        <hr style="width:50px;border:5px solid red" class="w3-round">
        <!-- Flex Container for Testimonial Cards -->
        <div class="w3-container w3-row-padding">
            <!-- Family Testimonial -->
            <div class="w3-col l4 m6 w3-margin-bottom">
                <div class="w3-card w3-padding">
                    <img src="/assets/Family.jpg" alt="Family Testimonial" style="width:100%; height: auto;">
                    <p class="w3-large w3-margin-top">"Scotbank has been a crucial part of our family's financial planning. Their personal touch and understanding of our needs have made banking a pleasant experience. We're grateful for their support and services." - Dave and Susan</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Student Testimonial -->
            <div class="w3-col l4 m6 w3-margin-bottom">
                <div class="w3-card w3-padding">
                    <img src="/assets/student.jpeg" alt="Student Testimonial" style="width:100%; height: auto;">
                    <p class="w3-large w3-margin-top">"As a student, managing finances can be daunting. Scotbank's friendly advice and easy-to-use banking app have made it so much simpler for me to manage my expenses and save for the future." - Rebecca, Student</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Business Owner Testimonial -->
            <div class="w3-col l4 m6 w3-margin-bottom">
                <div class="w3-card w3-padding">
                    <img src="/assets/bankers.jpeg" alt="Business Owner Testimonial" style="width:100%; height: auto;">
                    <p class="w3-large w3-margin-top">"At my business, Scotbank has been instrumental in providing financial solutions that align with our goals. Their expertise and commitment to our success make them an invaluable partner." - John</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- JavaScript and any additional scripts -->
<script>
    // Script to open and close sidebar
    function w3_open() {
        document.getElementById("mySidebar").style.display = "block";
        document.getElementById("myOverlay").style.display = "block";
    }

    function w3_close() {
        document.getElementById("mySidebar").style.display = "none";
        document.getElementById("myOverlay").style.display = "none";
    }


    // Modal Image Gallery
    function onClick(element) {
        document.getElementById("img01").src = element.src;
        document.getElementById("modal01").style.display = "block";
        var captionText = document.getElementById("caption");
        captionText.innerHTML = element.alt;
    }
</script>
</body>

</html>
